	<section>
		<header>OO jDREW Execution</header>
                 <p>The RuleML facts and rules can be combined into one rulebase
		 and executed bottom-up with the <a href="http://www.jdrew.org/oojdrew/">OO jDREW BU Engine</a>.</p>
	</section>
		
